<HEADLINE> Thai Woman Sets World Weightlifting Record </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
JAKARTA, October 13 (Xinhua) -- Thailand's Suta Kassaraporn
Monday set a weightlifting world record with a clean and jerk of
125 kilograms in the women's 59-kilogram division at the Southeast
Asia Games.
