today when both Indian President Kocheril Raman Narayanan and
Prime Minister Inder Kumar Gujral will be present.
</P>
<P>
During her stay here, the queen will also visit Amritsar of
Punjab, Chennai of Tamil Nadu and Kochi of Kelala.
</P>
<P>
This is the queen's third visit to India.  
